model

Class MoviesCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.MoviesCollection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DVDCollection, LaserDiscCollection, VHSCollection

    public class MoviesCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    MoviesCollection is a parent class to DVD, LasesrDisc, and VHS. It holds variables that each one of these classes have in common. Title: The title of this movie collectible. Year: The year this movie collectible was released. Genre: The genre of this movie collectible. Format: The format of this movie collectible (DVD, VHS, LD) Director: The director of this movie collectible. Special Edition: Whether this movie collectible was part of a special edition.
    Author:
    Travis Lawson
